body.p: The model reproduces the time profile of TOC1 and Y mRNA for a 8:16 cycle as depicted in Fig7A and 7B. A simple algorithm in the event section accomplishes the 8 hour light and 16 hour dark cycle. The model was successfully tested on MathSBML
